itedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:57:31.000Z","msg":"咩叫內地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T09:10:19.000Z","msg":"巴打少上呢度，佢五毛/工作人員來，仲自稱住廣州<br />\n<br />\n呢度時事台 五毛/工作人員回應比例一半以上"},{"pid":"851dcf3612321bc2ef3d7f35a0001c1e2e54548c","tid":671401,"uid":37066,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T09:13:52.000Z","msg":"本土講獨鍵國派可始唔講人權唔講普世價值，其實佢地就愈來愈似其產黨了"},{"pid":"7d73b9d0f508c142e727fd9422c457fbd8e78eda","tid":671401,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"851dcf3612321bc2ef3d7f35a0001c1e2e54548c","tid":671401,"uid":37066,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T09:13:52.000Z","msg":"本土講獨鍵國派可始唔講人權唔講普世價值，其實佢地就愈來愈似其產黨了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T09:18:21.000Z","msg":"你知唔知你打緊乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"086a4a8f3f932c9f881866976379eaadab3b32c4","tid":671401,"uid":9594,"like":5,"dislike":9,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T09:25:52.000Z","msg":"香港人本黎就得淡笑<br />\n<br />\n除了真正既原居民<br />\n<br />\n香港人係邊到黎？ <br />\n<br />\n咪又係支那走難落黎<br />\n<br />\n而集合咁多種走難黎既支那人共同基因係咩？<br />\n<br />\n咪就係走難賤種基因囉<br />\n<br />\n其中不外乎 自私自利 貪心怕死 欺善怕惡<br />\n<br />\n沒事就同你威啦威 有咩事當然走先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07f7cde8bc8ac61582f4c9c08940801a3af5de39","tid":671401,"uid":156659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T09:31:03.000Z","msg":"雖然依家都唔知有咩做可以去推動港獨，但至少都捐錢支持一班坐緊監嘅義士<br />\n另外唔好再信班泛民，依班仆街都係賣港賊"},{"pid":"57b597ba7bae3590693d8bac36aa2f63daa703c7","tid":671401,"uid":12633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"07f7cde8bc8ac61582f4c9c08940801a3af5de39","tid":671401,"uid":156659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T09:31:03.000Z","msg":"雖然依家都唔知有咩做可以去推動港獨，但至少都捐錢支持一班坐緊監嘅義士<br />\n另外唔好再信班泛民，依班仆街都係賣港賊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T09:56:47.000Z","msg":"係，我都有捐；<br />\n（同埋可以留意下近期既活動）"},{"pid":"813896aa344a12487398984ed39f2d63455ab902","tid":671401,"uid":37066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d73b9d0f508c142e727fd9422c457fbd8e78eda","tid":671401,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"851dcf3612321bc2ef3d7f35a0001c1e2e54548c","tid":671401,"uid":37066,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T09:13:52.000Z","msg":"本土講獨鍵國派可始唔講人權唔講普世價值，其實佢地就愈來愈似其產黨了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T09:18:21.000Z","msg":"你知唔知你打緊乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T10:28:50.000Z","msg":"on9仔先唔明我打緊咩"},{"pid":"7b834cabe832723d6ddf7edefd16b0243974ef9f","tid":671401,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cb90052822b48cce41e5162ba7b3380c3dbc4ff","tid":671401,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:16:14.000Z","msg":"正如彭定康講過：「我感到憂慮的，不是香港的自主權會被北京剝奪，而是這項權利會一點一滴地斷送在香港某些人手裏。」<br />\n<br />\n自雨傘革命失敗之後，越黎越多人變得灰心，開始政治冷感、專注搵錢 &mdash;&mdash; 其實同六四後既中國人一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而香港既公務員體系，以致高樓價高地價，就係政府最好既 維穩 手段。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n做左公務員既人，根本無可能反政府；<br />\n要供樓既人，根本無可能反政府；<br />\n佢地全部都係現今香港既得利益者，所以佢地只會說服自己，然後慢慢變成藍絲。<br />\n<br />\n由於香港既生活實在太艱難，越黎越多人只顧搵錢 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n&quot;要返工，不了&quot;<br />\n&quot;集會有咩用？不了&quot;<br />\n&quot;都阻止唔到架啦，不了&quot;<br />\n⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">因為失敗主義，我地其實已經對中國投降。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">中國既洗血係好快，但香港人轉變既速度更快</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地已經變得冷血，我地接受左梁天琦坐監，我地接受左一地兩檢，我地接受左香港政府出賣香港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢個時候一定有5毛話：&quot;唔接受，咁你有咩大計？&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">問題係你地撫心自問，有無真係諗過可以點樣做？你地撫心自問，有無真正支援過任何本土組織，例如捐錢去星火？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地根本就係冷漠，你地根本就係懶，你地根本就係毫無良知！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n係今時今刻，的確無任何反共大計，但係；<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">所有歷史既發生，都係需要時勢；如果時勢未到，我地心態已經變成蝗國人，咁就算到時出現左孫中山，又有咩用？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時勢，係需要慢慢建立，用五年、十年既時間；我地每一個所做既小小事，都有機會影響未來既發展。如果眾位香港人無咁既覺悟，係而家呢一刻就放棄，</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁你地同支那豬有咩分別？</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T10:31:17.000Z","msg":"又港豬？人哋係港豬，咁你哋係乜？"},{"pid":"fcdb1d8dcbf1e037ba1b606bafb77c0dbe6b328b","tid":671401,"uid":180258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b33793cf8e659728a4801d47a30945364290f52","tid":671401,"uid":12633,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"efaf1404455e803c82bac43d00887d0f97494980","tid":671401,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:56:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T07:01:09.000Z","msg":"香港內地，係咪指新界"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T12:22:14.000Z","msg":"NONONO<br />\n我住新界 勁多支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n周圍都係蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又大聲又臭又冇規矩冇禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日都忍唔住屌柒佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解變到咁。。<br />\n新界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係 內地！"},{"pid":"3be7dce9cd6a6c1b8ef6905be2d5433f981070dc","tid":671401,"uid":180258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T12:36:19.000Z","msg":"問題越來越嚴重既源頭係學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上而家小學生返學都係聽蝗語 因為大半班同學都係支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要而家又有洗腦教育 老師仲有啲係支那人<br />\n以前就話普教中 到而家係普教中、數、常識等等<br />\n其實就係除咗英文之後都係蝗語<br />\n小學生既吸收係最強 <br />\n當又有洗腦既愛國教又有啲支那自私同學仔既時候<br />\n好自然就變埋一樣咁自私自利 冇禮貌 唔識尊重。。。<br />\n當然亦都有啲真係知有問題既老師 <br />\n佢地會嘗試去糾正學生思想教返好佢地 但係唔多所以都比較難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人幾時先識醒識唸咩係啱同錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我對香港仲有希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果齊心我唸會可以事成 攞得返屬於香港人既野 有我地應有既香港🇭🇰我愛香港🎗❤️"},{"pid":"8fcca5c03aecb85691c7e9f0fa3c1f84f427e70e","tid":671401,"uid":28503,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T12:49:42.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過你班本土撚其實係小數<br />\n咪再搞搞陣啦 香港本來就係中國領土 變成中國一份子都係天經地義"},{"pid":"e63ca9abe71a5a8f301703ee9f39e81a84bdd9b9","tid":671401,"uid":180258,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8fcca5c03aecb85691c7e9f0fa3c1f84f427e70e","tid":671401,"uid":28503,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T12:49:42.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過你班本土撚其實係小數<br />\n咪再搞搞陣啦 香港本來就係中國領土 變成中國一份子都係天經地義"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T13:14:48.000Z","msg":"本來 唔該曬你喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4402cef7965ca4177e4e5021babe6421f6065fb","tid":671401,"uid":85461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T20:53:21.000Z","msg":"移民"},{"pid":"91da89e226aff1464ae659fb533de11988fc3f77","tid":671401,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T04:26:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d49113970acd02ba3ba3d939b0d3facc0b381041","tid":671401,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6bda443bc95692f80d1eae1c4e1d8b99d968eb64","tid":671401,"uid":12633,"like":69,"dislike":3,"score":66,"quote":{"pid":"b6628b9ab832e0edce3ecd9eb79d56c076ed36c4","tid":671401,"uid":149494,"like":12,"dislike":48,"score":-36,"citedBy":3,"r